entries.femaleVariant: Girl, your new nose is fabulous. I think it's your best yet. Hardly recognized you!
You should've seen me on set last week. Wardrobe swapped out everything. Even my voice.
They made me into this rippling stud, and oooh... I'd have blown myself if I could.
You know... I really shouldn't be telling you this... But I beat out Tom Bradley for the role!
Ooooh! Our girl is on fire!
Well, seems I'm almost all boy these days.
